Class BulkBarcodeConfigServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
com.agaramtech.qualis.bulkbarcodeconfiguration.service.BulkBarcodeConfigServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
BulkBarcodeConfigService
@Transactional(readOnly=true, rollbackFor=java.lang.Exception.class) @Service public class BulkBarcodeConfigServiceImpl extends Object implements BulkBarcodeConfigService
This class holds methods to perform CRUD operation on 'bulkbarcodeconfig','bulkbarcodeconfigdetails' table through its DAO layer.
